Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  有那么多人都赶到汤乃鹭来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为县外也有人过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  许愿板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  大家可都拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（存钱）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多东西  不觉得放弃还太早了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我现在到汤乃鹭了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我去接下阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要我开车送你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  你们先去雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子  真是个静不下来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她这么跑掉好么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为新干线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说我可是很现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个反面教材生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anything  去那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是say anything的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  妈妈  给我买苹果糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑  要买自己买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小气  跟绪花一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是她像我才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要五百万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让脚踝瘦下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是在把烦恼发泄出来而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做偷窥别人愿望这样恶趣味的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我想成为四十万翠  绪花）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像老板娘那样  对工作充满自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处事态度认真  却有些孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都不曾忘记自己最初的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曾忘记最早的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个梦想  不是我一个人就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是因为有许多人的雪愿照亮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正是因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必须雪愿才行  在各种方面上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花她不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看一下下没关系啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒哦  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦行啦鹤来同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不会少你一块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么紧要什么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（希望我有朝一日能够赶上彻先生  民子）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（作为一名厨师  希望能够更上一层楼  彻）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跑得再快些  可是赶不上我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身哦  女服务员的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃炒面！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  来一份炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:04:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好说出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路边摊的炒面给人一种特别的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常在店里吃的还有家里做的都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也喜欢路边摊的炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…阿孝！  非常喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场祭典能把所有的愿望带往天上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你离开以后  我本打算一个人继续往前冲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个以我为梦想的外孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话我想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要到儿子那边去住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我守在锅炉前  不意间已经过了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多我也该准备后事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿积累起来的重要回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算一个不漏地全带到棺材里去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向老板娘说一声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和孙子幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我说两句可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家也都能听一听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事让我明白了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还远远不够老练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说妈了  就连姐姐我都赶不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子咯  天生才能就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说过希望大家能跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还不是这块料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你要关喜翠庄这件事…我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是暂时关门而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我绝不会让喜翠庄就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多学习一些  多修炼一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有朝一日能够让旅馆重新开业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那个时候  再让我继承喜翠庄这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想开一家让妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老板娘喜悦的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  到那时候我也会帮你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  我也一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样  丢下老公也要来这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}诶  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们越笨越可爱呢  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今晚就尽情喝吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醉方休！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你也一块喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有成年…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  少装可爱了  这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不准长时间逗留哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想搞些什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可得乖乖给我打报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去偷窥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你接下来打算怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想暂时在熟人家里打扰一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟绪花一起来东京不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找一个能让我做女服务员混口饭吃的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混口饭吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起指使别人  自己干活更合我的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续做一个讨人厌的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢您  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床单的这里不折好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  在这么破的房间里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还和一个有点古怪的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过居然是白住…总感觉挺过意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人说我很少会邀朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个都高兴得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间旅馆果然超级棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆也是  这里工作的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得所谓的归宿啊  并不是一开始就在那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要自己找到  自己做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你我不免这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…会找到的  我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个归宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…我的…归宿…跟你的一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这里是我的房间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的男朋友人好像很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  只不过优柔寡断而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然输给那种男人  彻先生真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情不是输赢能说清的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没在老板娘房间里睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄里我的归宿是这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次摇熊铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节貌似熊会出没哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…便利店好远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕镇一圈的睡衣祭还将继续！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了买肉包了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑过自己为什么会那么执着于喜翠庄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…能一直和彻先生在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个没错…但才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…我的梦想…不知不觉间变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一心想着成为厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我想成为喜翠庄的厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想什么的…虽然还不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我希望能再回到喜翠庄来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这个许许多多的梦想诞生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…诞生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前就是在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用以前这种过去时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…在未来的某一天…就会在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄将作为汤乃鹭的历史建筑物保存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这段短暂的经历告别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这段悠久的历史告别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给你发邮件的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会去找你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个  不小心没赶上车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离下班火车还有些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好道一声别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这里…喜翠庄告别…一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘您知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边木板的纹理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看都像是个人脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边与其说是像人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次来到喜翠庄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这就像是故事中登场的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是不出意料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多故事般的趣事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都遇上不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这都是因为大家都在雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命努力的人聚集在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命雪愿的话  当然会发生各种各样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下故事的也正是大家一份一份的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪里  一定都能创造  故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会回到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就由你来代替电六记录这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我来代替豆丁老爷继续记录
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本业务日志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一定会回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会面总不能迟到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还一定只是花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能够仰望高高在上的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞开喉咙畅饮水分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正准备绽放呢
